Flask-BS4 Changelog
===================


Version 4.5.3.0
---------------

Released on October 21st 2020

-   Update Bootstrap to 4.5.2


Version 4.5.2.0
---------------

Released on September 23rd 2020

-   Update Bootstrap to 4.5.2
-   Update `popper.js` to 1.16.1
-   `DateTimeLocalField` added to sample app.
-   Add: Support forms with `MultipleFileField`.


Version 4.5.0.3
---------------

Released on August 27th 2020

-   ADD: `FieldList` is now displayed correctly
-   ADD: `FormField` is now displayed correctly
-   FIX: Display error messages under the fields


Version 4.5.0.2
---------------

Released on July 14th 2020

-   Fix(pagination): fix pagination classes (#6)


Version 4.5.0.1
---------------

Released on July 9th 2020

-   Fix Flask-Nav support updated to Bootstrap 4.x (#4)


Version 4.5.0.0
---------------

Released on May 20th 2020

-   Upgrade Bootstrap to 4.5.0
-   Upgrade jQuery to 3.5.1


Version 4.4.1.9
---------------

Released on May 15th 2020

-   Fix passing the enctype to the quick_form (#3)


Version 4.4.1.8
---------------

Released on April 29th 2020

-   Patch: Use `Markup.unescape` for fields instead of patching all other fields


Version 4.4.1.7
---------------

Released on April 26th 2020

-   Patch: WTForms Pull #400 uses Markupsafe
-   Create pythonpublish.yml
-   Git: Push tags to `origin` on release


Version 4.4.1.6
---------------

Released on February 25th 2020

-   Update: Sample app cleanup
-   Update: `setup.py` no longer lists support for v2
-   Update: Remove components
-   Update: Components `modal` renamed to `modals`
-   Add: `render_field` filter
-   Update: `render_form` uses `render_kw` with `xmlattr`
-   Update: `render_form` uses `render_kw`
-   Add: `cards` component
-   Fix: `quick_form` attributes cleanup
-   Fix: `render_form` uses `render_kw` as v3
-   Fix: `render_form` uses the manual `enctype`
-   Add: form can have `novalidate` attribute
-   Add: component `modal` with automatic button
-   Fix: Button `**kwargs` are used in component
-   Fix: button `type` maps to `design` for historic
-   Fix: `btn` components apply size
-   `quick_form` uses internally `render_form`
-   Set theme jekyll-theme-minimal


Version 4.4.1.5
---------------

Released on February 25th 2020

-   Add: Makefile
-   Add Validation to `render_form` (#1)
-   Add: Components.Modal with focus and button
-   Fix: `enctype` has no index if no `FileField`
-   Add: Components.Buttons in different variations
-   Modify sample app for `forms.render_form`
-   Fix: `forms.render_form` creates correct fields
-   Update .gitignore to ignore .vscode
-   Feature: Add Sample App to view the Input Fields


